snippet.title: Arcade Manager - Steam Next Fest: February 2025 Demo
snippet.description:
Build and manage the Arcade of your dreams. Unlock lots of fully animated games, set their jackpots and build prize zones. Start with a humble local arcade and expand into an major arcade entertainment center! Unlock Legend mods to change the rules and strategies of the game.

Developed by Prosper Forge
Release Date: March 29th, 2025
